  "description": "March legate-loop service health: liveness, queue depth (dispatchable/blocked/total), dispatch activity, workers, forwarded loop logs, and dispatch traces. Backed by march_legate_* (Prometheus), march-legate logs (Loki), and march-legate traces (Tempo). One container per profile/conductor.",
